name: Seeker Mastery Slate
description: Struck to recognize your achievement in reaching the rank of 10 - Seeker.

languages.description: Geschaffen, um dein Erreichen von Rang 10 - Suchender zu ehren.
languages.name: Meisterschaft-Insignie: Suchender

languages.description: Gravée pour commémorer votre réussite en atteignant le Palier 10 - Chercheur.
languages.name: Ardoise de Maîtrise - Chercheur

languages.description: Coniata per riconoscere il tuo successo nel raggiungere il grado 10 - Cercatore.
languages.name: Targa Maestria - Cercatore

languages.description: 랭크 10 - 시커에 도달한 업적을 기리기 위한 표창패입니다.
languages.name: 시커 마스터리 슬레이트

languages.description: Impresionado por reconocer tu logro al alcanzar el rango de 10 - Buscador.
languages.name: Placa de Maestría de Buscador

languages.description: 为表彰你成功达到段位 10－探求者所打造的物品。
languages.name: 探求者精通石板

languages.description: シーカー「マスタリーランク10」へ到達したテンノの成果を示す表彰楯。

languages.description: Stworzona, by upamiętnić Twój wyczyn w osiągnięciu rangi 10 - Poszukiwacz.

languages.description: Concedida em reconhecimento à sua conquista por alcançar o nível 10 - Predador.

languages.description: 篆刻來認可你達成精通段位 10－探求者的成就。

languages.description: ประทับตรารับรู้ถึงความสำเร็จของคุณในการไปถึงอันดับ 10 - นักแสวงหา
languages.name: กระดานชนวนความเชี่ยวชาญ: นักแสวงหา

languages.description: Seviye 10 - İzci seviyesine ulaşma başarını anmak için oluşturulmuştur.
languages.name: İzci Ustalık Plaketi
